    <item>
      <title>Hugo 博客标签与配置文件修改指南</title>
      <link>http://localhost:5307/enderman2710.github.io/post/hugo-tags-config-guide/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (enderman2710)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:5307/enderman2710.github.io/post/hugo-tags-config-guide/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>Hugo 博客标签与配置文件修改指南</h1><p>作者：enderman2710（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="hugo-博客标签与配置文件修改指南">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#hugo-%e5%8d%9a%e5%ae%a2%e6%a0%87%e7%ad%be%e4%b8%8e%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%ae%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6%e4%bf%ae%e6%94%b9%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%97"></a>
Hugo 博客标签与配置文件修改指南
</h1><h2 id="一给文章添加标签和分类">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%b8%80%e7%bb%99%e6%96%87%e7%ab%a0%e6%b7%bb%e5%8a%a0%e6%a0%87%e7%ad%be%e5%92%8c%e5%88%86%e7%b1%bb"></a>
一、给文章添加标签和分类
</h2><p>在 Hugo 中，标签 (<code>tags</code>) 和分类 (<code>categories</code>) 写在每篇文章的 <strong>front matter</strong>（文件头部的 <code>---</code> 区域）里。</p>
<h3 id="基本语法">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%9f%ba%e6%9c%ac%e8%af%ad%e6%b3%95"></a>
基本语法
</h3><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nn">---</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">title</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;你的文章标题&#39;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">date</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;2026-05-21&#39;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">tags</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;标签1&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;标签2&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;标签3&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">categories</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;分类名&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nn">---</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="标签-vs-分类">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%a0%87%e7%ad%be-vs-%e5%88%86%e7%b1%bb"></a>
标签 vs 分类
</h3><table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th></th>
          <th>分类 (categories)</th>
          <th>标签 (tags)</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>性质</td>
          <td>大类，一篇文章通常一个分类</td>
          <td>细粒度关键词，可以有多个</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>举例</td>
          <td>技术、生活、项目</td>
          <td>Hugo、Python、前端、教程</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>页面</td>
          <td><code>/categories/技术/</code></td>
          <td><code>/tags/Hugo/</code></td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="实际例子">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%ae%9e%e9%99%85%e4%be%8b%e5%ad%90"></a>
实际例子
</h3><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nn">---</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">title</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;我的技术文章&#39;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">date</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;2026-05-21&#39;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">tags</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;Python&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;Django&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;后端&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">categories</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;技术&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nn">---</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span></code></pre></div><p>添加后 Hugo 会自动生成：</p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-05-21首发于<a href='http://localhost:5307/enderman2710.github.io/'>enderman2710</a>，最后修改于2026-05-21</p>]]>
